**Psychedelic escape room where a player eats pills and relies on hallucinations to solve puzzles**

EARLY VERSION - CHEAPER PRICE!

Welcome to one of the most **unique** and **bizarre** VR experiences, where you take on the role of an investigator searching for a missing woman — and are forced to consume drugs during your mission...

{549486470892320}

 **The boundaries between reality, virtuality, and hallucinations dissolve,** immersing you in a **Lovecraftian nightmare.**

The only daughter of a retired businessman vanishes without a trace. Hired to investigate the case, the player discovers a seemingly abandoned laboratory. As you explore room after room, you uncover evidence of twisted experiments, scattered notebooks of employees, and disturbing accounts from test subjects. **The gameplay revolves around solving intricate puzzles while piecing together the unsettling truth of the past.**
{512873561581823}

Dive into a haunting world filled with **grotesque biotechnological machinery** and **the wicked remnants of dark experiments**.

{1160808341771416}

**Experience mind-bending psychedelic trips** that distort perception and twist your surroundings.

{526826886708992}

The goals of Early Access are to refine and enhance Dark Trip’s unique mechanics and to expand the game’s content through continuous feedback from our community.

Join our Discord channel to share your thoughts and help shape the game.

{1628601371154553}

**Enter the surreal horror.**
